⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Crocomire
node MET · MET · ⟦Crocomire:MET:621a89⟧

WHO   — Crocomire — the lava-beast
WHAT  — A grisly boss of Super Metroid — a fire-belching monster Samus drives steadily backward with her own fire until it topples into a pit of acid, where its flesh boils away from its skeleton before its dying weight collapses the wall behind it.
WHERE — MET · Metroid  Framework inputs: Super Metroid (1994)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because Norfair belongs to it, and nothing crosses its chamber unchallenged; because it is a sentinel of the deep heat, a living obstacle between the hunter and the secrets buried below.
HOW   — By bulk and fury and gouts of flame in the molten dark — driven back step by step into the acid not by raw damage but by the relentless pressure of Samus's weapons, until the floor gives way beneath it.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the beast of the burning deep — and I die the worst death in Zebes, flesh sloughed from bone in the acid.

